# Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration
# Enforce canonical URLs with trailing slashes for SEO

# Redirect www to non-www 
https://www.ride-more.org/* https://ride-more.org/:splat 301!
http://www.ride-more.org/* https://ride-more.org/:splat 301!

# Force HTTPS
http://ride-more.org/* https://ride-more.org/:splat 301!

# Add trailing slash to paths that don't have one (excluding files)
# This specifically targets the root and page paths
/docs /docs/ 301!
/blog /blog/ 301!
/contact /contact/ 301!
/discord /discord/ 301!

# Catch-all for root domain
https://ride-more.org https://ride-more.org/ 301!
